EXHIBIT D
JOINT FILING AGREEMENT

MFA FINANCIAL, INC. In accordance with Rule 13d-1(k) under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended, the undersigned hereby confirm the agreement by and
among them to the joint filing on behalf of them of the Statement on Schedule 13D and any and all further amendments thereto, with respect to the
securities of the above referenced issuer, and that this Agreement be included as an Exhibit to such filing.

This Agreement may be executed in any
number of counterparts each of which shall be deemed to be an original and all of which together shall be deemed to constitute one and the same
Agreement. IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the undersigned hereby execute this Agreement as of July 6, 2020.
